## "value language" model
| Property | Definition | Value type | Repeatable |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| value | String describing the language of the descriptive metadata value. | String | No |
| code | Code representing the language of the descriptive metadata value. | String | No |
| uri | URI for the language of the descriptive metadata value. | String | No |
| note | Other information related to the language of the descriptive metadata value. Note types must be from the "note" controlled list. | Object ("description" model) | Yes |
| source | The vocabulary, authority, or other origin for the language term and/or code. | Object ("source" model) | No |
| valueScript | An alphabet or other notation used to represent a language or other symbolic system of the descriptive metadata value. | Object ("value script" model) | No |
